Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.button

Class ButtonServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<ButtonComponentType,Button>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.button.ButtonServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ButtonService, TableInsertion
public class ButtonServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<ButtonComponentType,Button> implements ButtonService
Provides service-level operations for interacting with button components.

This class manages button interactions (clicks, state checks, and table insertions) by delegating to the appropriate Button implementation based on the provided ButtonComponentType.
